OL,3,CIncrease capital funding in spring
OL,4,CBudget, Robison urges Chancellor
OL,6,FScotland's Deputy First Minister has
OL,7,Furged the Chancellor to increase
OL,8,Ffunding for capital projects in his
OL,9,Fspring Budget.
OL,11,FWith the fiscal event due on
OL,12,FWednesday, Shona Robison has again
OL,13,Fpushed for an increase in funding to
OL,14,Fthe devolved administrations through
OL,15,FBarnett consequentials.
