OL,3,CIncrease capital funding in spring
OL,4,CBudget, Robison urges Chancellor
OL,6,F"Key to that is funding for
OL,7,Finfrastructure. We've already
OL,8,Fcommitted #6.3 billion of capital
OL,9,Fspending as part of the 2024-25
OL,10,FScottish Budget, underpinning high-
OL,11,Fquality public services, creating jobs
OL,12,Fand supporting the economy.
OL,14,F"However, we are expecting a real-
OL,15,Fterms cut to our UK capital funding of
OL,16,Falmost 10% over five years, totalling
OL,17,Faround #1.6 billion ` enough to build
OL,18,Fa large hospital.
