OL,3,CIncrease capital funding in spring
OL,4,CBudget, Robison urges Chancellor
OL,6,F"Likewise, our financial transactions
OL,7,Fbudget ` key to delivering affordable
OL,8,Fhousing ` has been cut by 62%.
OL,10,F"With the UK now in recession, capital
OL,11,Finvestment to kick-start economic
OL,12,Factivity is needed now more than ever.
OL,13,FInfrastructure is vital for jobs,
OL,14,Feconomic growth and the path to net
OL,15,Fzero.
OL,17,F"That's why I am urging the Chancellor
OL,18,Fto deliver the capital funding
OL,19,FScotland needs."
