OL,4,CBudget, Robison urges Chancellor
OL,6,FA spokesman for the UK Government
OL,7,Fsaid: "The Scottish Government is
OL,8,Fcurrently receiving a record #41
OL,9,Fbillion per year funding settlement
OL,10,Ffrom the UK Government ` the largest
OL,11,Fin the history of devolution and one
OL,12,Fthat was further topped up by
OL,13,Fdecisions taken at Autumn Statement.
OL,15,F"It can also borrow up to #450 million
OL,16,Ffor capital investment on top of this
OL,17,Frecord funding, and the UK Government
OL,18,Fhas agreed to inflation-proof that
OL,19,Flimit going forward."
